            h4 timer.getValue()
            p Returns an unsigned long of how many milliseconds that have passed since the start of the timer.
            h5 EXAMPLE SKETCH
            script(type="syntaxhighlighter", class="brush: cpp; gutter: false;")
              :cdata
                void loop() {
                  Serial.println(timer.getValue());
                }

